  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/3049bb1ded0b33b8cbfe459fcb627250.poster.avif?t=1695666820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/3049bb1ded0b33b8cbfe459fcb627250.webm?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/3049bb1ded0b33b8cbfe459fcb627250.mp4?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UNDER WAVES</strong> is a twin stick shooter inspired by 80's arcade games<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><br>• A tribute to classics like <strong>Asteroids</strong>, <strong>Space Invaders</strong> and <strong>Geometry Wars</strong>.<br>• Endless arcade gameplay.<br>• Battle your own highscore and <strong>global leaderboards</strong>.<br>• 80's inspired modern <strong>synthwave</strong> soundtrack.<br>• Twin-stick optimized controls. <br>• <strong>Replayable</strong>, short mini-game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/d06ec5cdeee2e081a4f40d41c18b19ed.poster.avif?t=1695666820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/d06ec5cdeee2e081a4f40d41c18b19ed.webm?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/d06ec5cdeee2e081a4f40d41c18b19ed.mp4?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master <strong>dash habilities</strong> to evade responsive enemy action.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/834736606ce378b56b28821ab103a056.poster.avif?t=1695666820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/834736606ce378b56b28821ab103a056.webm?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/834736606ce378b56b28821ab103a056.mp4?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect <strong>power-ups</strong>, multipliers and energy crystals to increase power<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/6693c7ff5b00ee7c824133e54d484f69.poster.avif?t=1695666820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/6693c7ff5b00ee7c824133e54d484f69.webm?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/6693c7ff5b00ee7c824133e54d484f69.mp4?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive <strong>increasing waves</strong> of radioactive lifeforms in an under water arena.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY:</h2><br>• Endless enemies spawn randomly, each run is different.<br>• Difficulty increases along with progressing waves.<br>• <strong>A quirk:</strong> you are always slowly dying from radiation, get crystals to recharge your energy.<br>• Power-ups, multipliers and 9 different enemies.<br>• Quite short runs. Addicting <strong>\"just one more run\"</strong> gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/da7f812d178a54115b38aabed0d38f5a.poster.avif?t=1695666820\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/da7f812d178a54115b38aabed0d38f5a.webm?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977550/extras/da7f812d178a54115b38aabed0d38f5a.mp4?t=1695666820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UNDER WAVES</strong> will be available soon. <strong>WISHLIST NOW!</strong><br><br><br>Soundtrack by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio.",
